-- Ormat Industries Gains Most in Six Months After Sale, Profit
-- B y   C l a u d i a   M a e d l e r
-- 2012-03-18T14:55:19Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-03-18/ormat-industries-gains-most-in-six-months-after-sale-profit-1-.html
Ormat Industries Ltd. (ORMT)  gained the
most since September after the developer of geothermal power
plants agreed to sell a stake and reported a fourth-quarter loss
that narrowed.  The  shares  jumped 6.5 percent, the biggest surge since
Sept. 27, to 18 shekels at the 4:30 p.m. close in  Tel Aviv .  Fimi Opportunity Funds will purchase a 12 percent stake in
Ormat for about 297 million shekels ($79 million). Ormat said it
will sell about 13.7 million shares for 21.7 shekels each.  Separately, the company said it had a fourth-quarter loss
of $24.9 million after a loss of $44.3 million a year earlier.  To contact the reporter on this story:
